        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Born Gillian Matthews to a minor lord outsode of London. Her family died of the pox, but fate decreed a different path for her. A wealthy gentleman purchased her from the house master and took her home. She served as the Ventrue Lord Harrison Brewster's blood doll until her sixteenth birthday. She was educated and polished for her trouble. She was sent from his house to serve as the blood doll for antoher lord, and then another. The process repeated until she was 26 years old when she was embraced by Lady Cecily Gowan, her latest Domitor. Lady Cecily, upon notice of how human Gillian's features remained, set her to the task of learning to be a courtesan. She was further educated in the arts and began attending salons and dramas. She caught the eye of Lords, Barons, and even a Duke. She managed to parlet her looks and social grace into a business acumen and social dominance. She thrived in the social court of the princes of London and managed to garner numerous accolades to herself and her lineage. Recently Gillian has had several bad turns of fate; she was involved in several minor scandals that, while not getting her banished, did get her uninvited from several events. The greatest problem with London court is everyone is old; they all remember when you messed up and that you did so. They do not let that go for centuries. Gillian was offered a chance by Lady Cecily and her line to reclocate to LA and start anew. They would ensure she is established there, and merely need reports of the goings on in the city. Gillian knows there has to be more that isnot said, but it was too good a chance to pass up."
        ],
